des: Tickle math is the perfect approach to introduce preschoolers and kindergartners to math. The idea is to play, learn math, and laugh at the same time. For once they will feel good when they crack the questions. And when they get it wrong, they get tickled by the parents. All in all, there is never a dull moment when playing tickle math.
